  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下反欺诈系统的数据流向。核心是FinTech_FraudDetection模块，它要从账本服务获取数据，但同时账本服务又依赖认证中心。这个结构得画清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，FinTech_FraudDetection作为上游，FinTech_LedgerService在中间层，FinTech_AuthVault在最底层支撑。方向都是向上反馈对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，都是反向依赖。不过LedgerService不只是被动接收，它还要主动输出三类数据：反欺诈结果回写给FraudDetection，紧急交易和常规交易分别进两个不同的队列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我这样安排：FraudDetection在左，LedgerService居中，AuthVault在右形成主干。然后从LedgerService向右分出三条支路，分别是RES、EMG和NYSDEC。这样布局比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，RES那条线我理解，但EMG和NYSDEC都是FinTech_TransactionQueue，会不会让人误以为是同一个队列？其实一个是紧急队列，一个是纽约州合规队列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，虽然类型相同，但实例不同，我会用不同标签区分。EMG标注为紧急交易队列，NYSDEC标注为州级合规队列。那主干的三层结构我先画出来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，主干用反向箭头，LedgerService指向FraudDetection，AuthVault指向LedgerService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "主干完成了。现在加上三条输出线：RES返回FraudDetection，EMG和NYSDEC分别指向两个交易队列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，RES的箭头方向反了。RES是LedgerService输出给FraudDetection的结果，不是FraudDetection给LedgerService。你刚才画的是反向依赖的样式，但RES是正向的数据流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "NFWB"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修正了，RES现在是从LedgerService指向FraudDetection的单向箭头。那EMG和NYSDEC也是同样的正向数据流对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这三条都是LedgerService主动推送出去的。EMG走紧急通道，NYSDEC走合规审查通道，RES是风险评分回写。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC",
        "RES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下最终结构：左起FraudDetection，反向依赖LedgerService，LedgerService再反向依赖AuthVault；同时LedgerService正向输出到RES、EMG、NYSDEC三个下游。布局采用从左到右的横向流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。这样一眼就能看出：认证支撑账本，账本支撑反欺诈，同时账本又向外输出三类数据。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
